    "function_v0": {
      "doc": "CAP-0058 atomic constructor. Runs exactly once inside the deploy\\ntransaction \\xe2\\x80\\x94 no two-step window, no front-run vector.\\n\\nDo NOT re-add an \"already initialized\" guard; the protocol guarantees\\nsingle-call semantics by construction and the check would consume CPU\\nbudget on every deploy for no safety gain.\\n\\n# Arguments\\n- `admin`   \\xe2\\x80\\x94 The address authorized to mint (ZmokeAgent's distributor key)\\n- `decimal` \\xe2\\x80\\x94 Token precision. Use `7` to match XLM/USDC Stellar conventions.\\n- `name`    \\xe2\\x80\\x94 Full token name, e.g. `\"ZMOKE Loyalty Token\"`\\n- `symbol`  \\xe2\\x80\\x94 Ticker, e.g. `\"ZMOKE\"`",
      "name": "__constructor",
      "inputs": [
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "admin",
          "type_": "address"
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "decimal",
          "type_": "u32"
